<emphasis bold="true" pageId="255" pageNumber="256">CAN</emphasis>
: AB, MB, NT, SK
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="255" pageNumber="256" type="note">
<paragraph pageId="255" pageNumber="256">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="255" pageNumber="256">
This subspecies intergrades with the 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="255" pageNumber="256">nympha</emphasis>
form along a narrow zone in central Alberta (Pearson et al. 2006: 76).
</paragraph>
